{"id":147120,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/04/简讯：澳总理访问日本灾区/","date":"2011-04-24T07:00:27Z","modified":"2011-04-24T07:00:27Z","title":"简讯：澳总理访问日本灾区","content":"<div>\n<p>星期六（4月23日），澳大利亚总理吉拉德访问了日本地震灾区。</p>\n<p>据日本共同社报道，吉拉德访问了地震和海啸的重灾区日本宫城县的一个村，慰问并鼓励了灾民。</p>\n<p>日本外相松本刚明陪同访问。这是第一次有外国首脑访问日本灾区。</p>\n<p>吉拉德3天前抵达日本，在东京与首相菅直人举行了会谈，并会见了日本天皇夫妇。</p>\n</p></div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>\t<a href=\"http://www.bbc.co.uk/zhongwen/simp/world/2011/04/#page-top\" rel=\"nofollow\"><br />\n\t\t<span>点击</span><br />\n\t\t<span>页首</span><br />\n\t</a></div>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/GN4iI_Ls_kL8TkyxLdvb7pFZ3BI/0/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/GN4iI_Ls_kL8TkyxLdvb7pFZ3BI/0/di\"></a><br />\n<a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/GN4iI_Ls_kL8TkyxLdvb7pFZ3BI/1/da\"><img border=\"0\" ismap src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/GN4iI_Ls_kL8TkyxLdvb7pFZ3BI/1/di\"></a></p>\n<p><img height=\"1\" src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/cnbbc/~4/uzqq2RTGgd4\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"750556\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":176,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}